            "title": "五角大樓：已經通知Anthropic其對美國供應鏈構成風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"五角大樓：已經通知Anthropic其對美國供應鏈構成風險\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yFQHrtLRrw6C7iVW5kf5fQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/ef814150-18ec-11f1-bedb-9c707e33d210\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">五角大樓：已經通知Anthropic其對美國供應鏈構成風險</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
